Little did I know about the people behind these operations.  However, I started to follow them,  researched what they are doing — I decided to base most of my investment around people and their ambitions.  

It led me to Spencer Gore.   A man with flying aircraft ambitions which led me to Kent Wilson.   

When you start to put things into preceptive based on little evidence you begin to see the potential.   Alpine is doing prototype for $AAPL and has Tesla is a client.    

Everything is always somehow connected to something else.   Alpine 4 could be structuring its business in order to build the next biggest thing.   After EV’s and drone’s.  What could it be?  

So dear investor— don’t be dismayed.  Believe in the future.
